						<h4 class="fw-6 fs-33 font-sec color-dark-3 mb-16">Visibilité maximal</h4>
						<p class="fs-16 color-gray-4 font-sec lh-130 mb-24">Discover a hassle-free way to buy,
							                                    sell, or rent your dream property with our all-in-one real estate solution.</p>
						<a href="./properties.html" class=" real-btn bordered text-capitalize">Place an add</a>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 col-12 offset-lg-0 offset-md-3">
